  <data key="d2">제갈량 is a CSO agent responsible for overseeing strategy and managing multiple editors and their tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;제갈량 is a person involved in the Shared/ONZ Creator collaboration, with specific tasks indicated in the context.&lt;SEP&gt;제갈량 is the Chief Strategy Officer (CSO) overseeing the ORBI system's strategy and is responsible for coordination among various agent skills.&lt;SEP&gt;제갈량은 저장 경로의 한 부분으로, 특정 프로젝트 관련 콘텐츠를 관리하는 역할을 한다.&lt;SEP&gt;제갈량 is a session participant whose reports and activities are documented for tracking progress.&lt;SEP&gt;제갈량 is a character invoked using specific keywords in Claude Code for strategic analysis tasks.</data>
