<node id="Data Keeper">
  <data key="d0">Data Keeper</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Data Keeper handles the status of data channels and GitHub actions, focusing on collaborative automation tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Keeper is a centralized data collection gateway for advertising and sales metrics, facilitating regular data-related tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Keeper is a data management tool used by Golmani to analyze financial data and compute KPIs.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Keeper is a script used to process and clean data related to Shopify orders and Amazon's fulfillment status.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Keeper is associated with the integration of data collection processes within the system.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Keeper refers to the script `tools/data_keeper.py`, which is designed to collect and process data but has several identified issues.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Keeper is a script functioning as a central data collection and caching gateway, interfacing with various APIs.</data>
