<node id="Approval Send">
  <data key="d0">Approval Send</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The Approval Send workflow is among those that merged into the WJ TEST environment and have experienced a change in node count.&lt;SEP&gt;Approval Send is a workflow event that is linked to the Draft Generation and Reply Handler processes.&lt;SEP&gt;Approval Send is a workflow in the n8n platform that manages the sending of draft content for approval to relevant parties.&lt;SEP&gt;Approval Send is a workflow for sending approvals that functions on a 1-minute polling interval and is currently active.&lt;SEP&gt;Approval Send is a workflow that sends requests for approval of content.</data>
