<node id="Daily Budget">
  <data key="d0">Daily Budget</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Daily Budget pertains to the allocated spending amount for a campaign on a daily basis, which is advised to be less than five times the CPA.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba6de65dea0c52394963037230c64351</data>
