<node id="Budget">
  <data key="d0">Budget</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Budget indicates the total financial resources allocated for a campaign, advised to be at least $50 per day for effective performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Budget pertains to the allocated funds for ad sets, which can be influenced by audience overlap.&lt;SEP&gt;Budget in advertising refers to the allocation of financial resources for campaigns across different platforms.</data>
