<node id="Bid Cap">
  <data key="d0">Bid Cap</data>
  <data key="d1">strategy</data>
  <data key="d2">Bid Cap is a bidding strategy focused on strict cost control by setting a cap at 2x to 3x the target CPA.&lt;SEP&gt;Bid Cap is a manual bidding strategy that sets a maximum bid across auctions based on predicted conversion rates.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f8083e1466c400ead556f945e1c01b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea8e2d818e409b55995564c5e7a850fc</data>
