  <data key="d0">ROAS Goal</data>
  <data key="d1">strategy</data>
  <data key="d2">ROAS Goal is a strategy used primarily in e-commerce to optimize for revenue tracking with the requirement of a purchase event and dynamic values.&lt;SEP&gt;ROAS Goal is a goal-based bidding strategy aimed at maintaining a target return on ad spend.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f8083e1466c400ead556f945e1c01b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea8e2d818e409b55995564c5e7a850fc</data>
