  <data key="d0">Highest Value</data>
  <data key="d1">strategy</data>
  <data key="d2">Highest Value is a bidding strategy that prioritizes high-value conversions, particularly in campaigns with diverse products.&lt;SEP&gt;Highest Value is a spend-based bidding strategy focused on maximizing the purchase value of sold items.</data>
