<node id="Target CPA">
  <data key="d0">Target CPA</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Target CPA is a bidding strategy that aims to optimize cost per acquisition based on historical conversion data.&lt;SEP&gt;Target CPA is a measurable goal representing the cost per acquisition that advertisers aim for, typically set between 1.1-1.2 times historical values.</data>
