  <data key="d0">Consent Mode v2</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Consent Mode v2 is a mandatory framework for handling user consent regarding the use of data in the EU and EEA effective March 2024.&lt;SEP&gt;Consent Mode v2 is a compliance mechanism that ensures tracking practices adhere to regulations when serving European Union audiences.&lt;SEP&gt;Consent Mode v2 is a mandatory compliance feature enabling conversion modeling for users who have not granted consent for tracking.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-be2e77824c689c78138e4092cfb92169&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-abc482d1d7accb22469a33ba2864c773&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37362d4e6491b4d57d876569ea0c2316</data>
