  <data key="d2">Offline Conversion Import allows for importing offline lead generation data to Google Ads.&lt;SEP&gt;Offline Conversion Import is a method used in Google Ads to integrate lead generation data from CRM systems for effective tracking.&lt;SEP&gt;Offline Conversion Import is a method used for integrating CRM data related to closed deals and opportunities in advertising platforms.</data>
