  <data key="d0">Event Match Quality (EMQ)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Event Match Quality (EMQ) Scoring helps evaluate the effectiveness and accuracy of event tracking in advertising.&lt;SEP&gt;EMQ refers to the scoring system that evaluates the quality of matched events in advertising, influencing optimization and performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Event Match Quality (EMQ) measures the accuracy of matched events between pixels and other data sources.</data>
