  <data key="d0">Event Deduplication</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Event deduplication is the process of ensuring that events are not double-counted, particularly important for accurate conversion tracking.&lt;SEP&gt;Event Deduplication refers to processes that prevent counting an event multiple times by ensuring event identifiers are matched.</data>
