  <data key="d0">Amazon PPC</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Amazon PPC refers to the pay-per-click advertising strategy used by Amazon sellers to optimize their bids and budgets based on various data sources.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon PPC refers to advertising campaigns on Amazon linked to advertisement performance evaluation.</data>
