  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Shopify DTC (Direct-to-Consumer) is a sales model allowing brands to sell directly to customers through the Shopify platform.&lt;SEP&gt;Shopify DTC represents direct-to-consumer sales platforms on specified websites like onzenna.com and zezebaebae.com.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49ece9a987ad279e3e4a53aaf6e064e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1efb1619fcde847aac3e5ab03910161e</data>
