<node id="Golmani Full-Cost Margin Framework">
  <data key="d0">Golmani Full-Cost Margin Framework</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Golmani Full-Cost Margin Framework is a profitability analysis method used to determine the sustainable advertising cost of sales (ACOS) based on various cost factors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49ece9a987ad279e3e4a53aaf6e064e0</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__amazon-ppc-agent__ref__cross-platform-analysis.md</data>
