<node id="Contribution Margin">
  <data key="d0">Contribution Margin</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Contribution Margin is a financial metric used to assess the profitability of individual products by calculating the difference between sales revenue and variable costs.&lt;SEP&gt;Contribution Margin is a metric used to measure the profitability of a product after variable costs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49ece9a987ad279e3e4a53aaf6e064e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5de8e1dcf9a61dbf421e8d14c5dfb81</data>
