<node id="Amazon Ads Daily">
  <data key="d0">Amazon Ads Daily</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Amazon Ads Daily is a data source that tracks daily advertising metrics such as spend, sales, clicks, and impressions for Amazon advertising campaigns.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Ads Daily is a daily metric or dataset that evaluates the performance of advertisements run on Amazon.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Ads Daily refers to the daily data reporting service provided by Amazon Ads, tracking advertisement performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Ads Daily is a data collection channel that, when interrupted, causes issues in PPC analysis and ad spending.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Ads Daily is a data table that shows daily advertising costs associated with the Amazon platform, including cost and date.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Ads Daily provides campaign metrics and is part of the PPC data synced as of December 2025.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49ece9a987ad279e3e4a53aaf6e064e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ba82b6f6df3933f41b431b09c763aa4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9045580874b7de041dd5bcb4789c8f55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02605b24559815326965c5ae77ce411&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c7c8f4ec6c0120d6139491b839153b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-424e3fa906dd3057ca5f496e51b4558f</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__amazon-ppc-agent__ref__cross-platform-analysis.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__communicator.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__data-keeper.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__data-modeler.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__golmani__ref__orbi-business-context.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314139</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Google Ads Daily">
  <data key="d0">Google Ads Daily</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Google Ads Daily is a data source that captures daily advertising metrics including spend, conversion value, clicks, and impressions for Google Ads campaigns.&lt;SEP&gt;Google Ads Daily is a daily metric or dataset that tracks the performance of advertisements on Google services.&lt;SEP&gt;Google Ads Daily refers to the daily data reporting service provided by Google Ads for user engagement tracking.&lt;SEP&gt;Google Ads Daily is a data collection channel affected by interruptions, resulting in missed advertising expenditure.&lt;SEP&gt;Google Ads Daily refers to a data table that captures daily advertising expenses on the Google platform, detailing costs and associated dates.&lt;SEP&gt;Google Ads Daily refers to a dataset that provides daily performance metrics for advertising campaigns via the Google Ads API.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49ece9a987ad279e3e4a53aaf6e064e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ba82b6f6df3933f41b431b09c763aa4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9045580874b7de041dd5bcb4789c8f55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02605b24559815326965c5ae77ce411&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c7c8f4ec6c0120d6139491b839153b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8964ad7b95da832e458de5ac218c90ab</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__amazon-ppc-agent__ref__cross-platform-analysis.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__communicator.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__data-keeper.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__data-modeler.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__golmani__ref__kpi-data-taxonomy.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314126</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Meta Ads Daily">
  <data key="d0">Meta Ads Daily</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Meta Ads Daily is a data source that monitors daily metrics such as spend, purchase value, purchases, and reach for Meta advertising campaigns.&lt;SEP&gt;Meta Ads Daily is a daily metric or dataset that assesses the performance of advertisements on platforms owned by Meta.&lt;SEP&gt;Meta Ads Daily tracks advertisement performance using data from the Graph API.&lt;SEP&gt;Meta Ads Daily is a channel that becomes unavailable for analysis if data collection fails.&lt;SEP&gt;Meta Ads Daily refers to a data table that tracks daily expenses related to advertising on the Meta platform, detailing spend and date.&lt;SEP&gt;Meta Ads Daily is a dataset that contains daily reporting fields for advertisements run through the Meta Marketing API.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49ece9a987ad279e3e4a53aaf6e064e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ba82b6f6df3933f41b431b09c763aa4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9045580874b7de041dd5bcb4789c8f55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02605b24559815326965c5ae77ce411&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c7c8f4ec6c0120d6139491b839153b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8964ad7b95da832e458de5ac218c90ab</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__amazon-ppc-agent__ref__cross-platform-analysis.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__communicator.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__data-keeper.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__data-modeler.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__golmani__ref__kpi-data-taxonomy.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314126</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Shopify Orders Daily">
  <data key="d0">Shopify Orders Daily</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Shopify Orders Daily is a data source that tracks daily metrics including gross sales, net sales, discounts, and units sold for DTC sales through Shopify.&lt;SEP&gt;Shopify Orders Daily is a daily metric or dataset that tracks daily orders processed through the Shopify platform.&lt;SEP&gt;Shopify Orders Daily tracks daily order data through its Admin REST API.&lt;SEP&gt;Shopify Orders Daily is impacted by data collection failures, obstructing revenue and discount rate calculations.&lt;SEP&gt;Shopify Orders Daily refers to a data table that tracks daily sales metrics including net sales and orders, categorized by brand and date.&lt;SEP&gt;Shopify Orders Daily is a dataset that classified all Amazon-tagged orders, leading to inflated metrics until corrections were made.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49ece9a987ad279e3e4a53aaf6e064e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ba82b6f6df3933f41b431b09c763aa4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9045580874b7de041dd5bcb4789c8f55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02605b24559815326965c5ae77ce411&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c7c8f4ec6c0120d6139491b839153b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa1a626b4d825367f61deb893c8e9257</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__amazon-ppc-agent__ref__cross-platform-analysis.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__communicator.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__data-keeper.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__data-modeler.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__kpi-monthly.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314229</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Amazon Sales Daily">
  <data key="d0">Amazon Sales Daily</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Amazon Sales Daily is a data source that reports daily metrics on gross sales, net sales, units, and fees associated with Amazon sellers.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Sales Daily is a daily metric or dataset that monitors the sales performance of products on Amazon.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Sales Daily is a data collection channel that reports missed sales figures for three sellers when disrupted.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Sales Daily is a data table that captures daily sales metrics such as ordered revenue, units sold, and date for the Amazon brand.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Sales Daily represents the daily sales data specific to Amazon channel sales used for monitoring performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Amazon Sales Daily is a dataset that contains actual sales data from Amazon but lacks detailed line-item information and discount breakdown.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-49ece9a987ad279e3e4a53aaf6e064e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ba82b6f6df3933f41b431b09c763aa4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d02605b24559815326965c5ae77ce411&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c7c8f4ec6c0120d6139491b839153b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e216433e87e27df18023b92896cdd9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aa1a626b4d825367f61deb893c8e9257</data>
