<node id="Seasonal Cross-Platform Patterns">
  <data key="d0">Seasonal Cross-Platform Patterns</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Seasonal Cross-Platform Patterns refer to the trends in advertising performance and consumer behavior across different times of the year.&lt;SEP&gt;Seasonal Cross-Platform Patterns refers to a concept that identifies how different advertising platforms react to specific seasons and events.</data>
