<node id="Auditor">
  <data key="d0">Auditor</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">An Auditor is an independent reviewer with a dual qualification from AICPA and KICPA, responsible for validating financial data through a comprehensive checklist.&lt;SEP&gt;The Auditor is an independent evaluator who verifies outputs in accordance with AICPA/KICPA standards.&lt;SEP&gt;The auditor role involves financial auditing responsibilities as part of evaluating financial practices.&lt;SEP&gt;The Auditor is an independent evaluator who reviews Golmani's output and ensures compliance with financial standards.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bcdebc0475d4243fd4d254986b49391c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-834ba5f6dae18383c4ff63198c6f5143&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-40386356c89e5a402a0f2a48e4cdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ebc11c230ce97c55325c82f7c5946993</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__auditor.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__cfo.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__제갈량.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__cfo_financial_review.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315237</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="AICPA">
  <data key="d0">AICPA</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The AICPA, or American Institute of Certified Public Accountants, is a professional organization representing accountants in the United States.&lt;SEP&gt;The AICPA is the American Institute of Certified Public Accountants, providing standards and guidance for auditing and accounting.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bcdebc0475d4243fd4d254986b49391c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ebc11c230ce97c55325c82f7c5946993</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__auditor.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__cfo_financial_review.md</data>
