  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="KICPA">
  <data key="d0">KICPA</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The KICPA, or Korean Institute of Certified Public Accountants, is a professional organization for accountants in South Korea.&lt;SEP&gt;The KICPA is the Korean Institute of Certified Public Accountants, also involved in standardizing auditing processes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bcdebc0475d4243fd4d254986b49391c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ebc11c230ce97c55325c82f7c5946993</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__auditor.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__cfo_financial_review.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315238</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Golmani">
  <data key="d0">Golmani</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Golmani is referred to as the source of financial data that the Auditor independently reviews without reliance on Golmani's explanations.&lt;SEP&gt;Golmani is the Vice President of Financial Modeling who generates outputs that are verified by the CFO and Auditor.&lt;SEP&gt;Golmani is an investment banker senior analyst agent who builds financial models and creates investor materials.&lt;SEP&gt;Golmani is an organization involved in investment analysis and modeling.&lt;SEP&gt;Golmani is the financial modeling VP tasked with generating financial reports and calculations based on directives from the CFO.&lt;SEP&gt;Golmani is responsible for producing outputs related to CFO directives and ensuring corrections are made based on audit findings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bcdebc0475d4243fd4d254986b49391c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-834ba5f6dae18383c4ff63198c6f5143&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d85ab4a566d07a836738ff78b108520&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-40386356c89e5a402a0f2a48e4cdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ebc11c230ce97c55325c82f7c5946993&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a53e9337bdf20e7f3e970fd6d648713e</data>
