<node id="CFO">
  <data key="d0">CFO</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The CFO is the Chief Financial Officer responsible for overseeing financial operations and approvals within the organization.&lt;SEP&gt;The CFO is the Chief Financial Officer and the orchestrator who oversees Golmani and coordinates with the Auditor for independent verification of outputs.&lt;SEP&gt;CFO refers to the Chief Financial Officer orchestrator role within the financial domain of the system.&lt;SEP&gt;The CFO is the Chief Financial Officer responsible for orchestrating the financial review workflow and making decisions based on audit results.&lt;SEP&gt;The CFO is the chief financial officer who provides directives and makes decisions based on the audit reports and Golmani's outputs.&lt;SEP&gt;CFO is the Chief Financial Officer responsible for overseeing financial reporting and ensuring compliance.&lt;SEP&gt;CFO refers to the Chief Financial Officer responsible for overseeing the financial audit documented in the report.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-834ba5f6dae18383c4ff63198c6f5143&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a2a416ce8319befb6569970717351ac6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-40386356c89e5a402a0f2a48e4cdf02d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ebc11c230ce97c55325c82f7c5946993&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a53e9337bdf20e7f3e970fd6d648713e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82d5e6384ec2e39cd8d8e05a2bc453df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d72451c08459b00c6cd8799579d3874d</data>
