  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">GitHub Actions is a continuous integration and continuous deployment tool designed to automate workflows, such as sending emails and tracking histories.&lt;SEP&gt;GitHub Actions is a framework for automating the workflow execution according to specified schedules.&lt;SEP&gt;GitHub Actions automate workflows, particularly for data collection and application deployments related to the Data Keeper.&lt;SEP&gt;GitHub Actions is a CI/CD platform that automates tasks for the Syncly data synchronization and scheduling.&lt;SEP&gt;GitHub Actions is a CI/CD tool allowing automatic execution of workflows, such as sending daily YouTube videos to Teams.</data>
