<node id="Firecrawl">
  <data key="d0">Firecrawl</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Firecrawl is a tool that facilitates web searching and content scraping, allowing the automation of data retrieval and processing.&lt;SEP&gt;Firecrawl is a web operations tool that optimizes web, browsing, scraping, and research tasks with high accuracy and speed using LLM-optimized output.&lt;SEP&gt;Firecrawl is a web scraping tool that allows users to extract data from websites using various scrape and crawl options.&lt;SEP&gt;Firecrawl is a tool utilized for web scraping and data extraction, providing various output formats.&lt;SEP&gt;Firecrawl is involved in web scraping and research processes, enhancing data gathering strategies.</data>
