<node id="Excel">
  <data key="d0">Excel</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Excel is a spreadsheet software used for formatting and presenting data effectively.&lt;SEP&gt;Excel is a spreadsheet software used for organizing and parsing data as part of the Resource Finder's output requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Excel is a spreadsheet application used for handling data, consisting of a main data sheet and summary sheets.&lt;SEP&gt;Excel format is used for outputting the keyword volume data with summary and detail sheets provided by the API.&lt;SEP&gt;Excel is a spreadsheet application by Microsoft, with a local backup path provided in the document for template management.&lt;SEP&gt;Excel is used to record vacation requests and cancellations detected by the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4295e963801c7018e84e3d8b7b0fad50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d7c07af37da7e5a5309a78b4b1227b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e47649c5461e27e5fc98ea375f13ba3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f0a3ef5bd61e4c7798e1d1b1d2c67beb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ccccaedca4b5b6188428dd006f19eb60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9935ebbb9b20f5976a156f23482e4e69</data>
