  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">LittlefingerUSA Inc. is a business entity located in Korea that is part of ORBI's US entities.&lt;SEP&gt;LittlefingerUSA Inc. is an exporting and importing company based in Korea, referred to as LFU.&lt;SEP&gt;LittlefingerUSA Inc., abbreviated as LFU, operates as an exporter or buyer/importer.&lt;SEP&gt;LittlefingerUSA Inc. is an exporter/importer mentioned in the entity quick reference.</data>
