<node id="Walk by Faith">
  <data key="d0">Walk by Faith</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Walk by Faith is the fulfillment service provider located in Cypress, CA, responsible for logistics of ORBI’s products.&lt;SEP&gt;Walk by Faith is a 3PL (third-party logistics provider) based in California, USA, referred to as WBF and acts as a final consignee.&lt;SEP&gt;Walk by Faith, abbreviated as WBF, acts as a final consignee.&lt;SEP&gt;Walk by Faith is listed as the final consignee in the entity quick reference.</data>
