<node id="Revenue">
  <data key="d0">Revenue</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Revenue is a monthly KPI tracked in the dashboard to assess financial performance against the plan.&lt;SEP&gt;Revenue is the total income generated from sales before deducting any expenses.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-565e3686182be6732f4eb713f7aefecc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5de8e1dcf9a61dbf421e8d14c5dfb81</data>
