  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Gross Margin">
  <data key="d0">Gross Margin</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Gross Margin is a monthly KPI reflecting the difference between revenue and the cost of goods sold.&lt;SEP&gt;Gross Margin refers to the income remaining after deducting the cost of goods sold (COGS), which is critical for audit verification.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-565e3686182be6732f4eb713f7aefecc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d72451c08459b00c6cd8799579d3874d</data>
