</node>
<node id="EBITDA">
  <data key="d0">EBITDA</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">EBITDA is a monthly KPI that indicates earnings before interest, taxes, depreciation, and amortization, compared to planned expectations.&lt;SEP&gt;EBITDA is Earnings Before Interest, Taxes, Depreciation, and Amortization, representing a company's operating performance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-565e3686182be6732f4eb713f7aefecc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5de8e1dcf9a61dbf421e8d14c5dfb81</data>
