<node id="Net Revenue">
  <data key="d0">Net Revenue</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Net Revenue is the income left after deducting discounts, returns, and COGS from gross revenue.&lt;SEP&gt;Net Revenue represents the profit earned after all expenses and deductions have been accounted for.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d5de8e1dcf9a61dbf421e8d14c5dfb81&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d7127bfda8dc54bd1f2b53807d426a2</data>
