</node>
<node id="COGS">
  <data key="d0">COGS</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">COGS stands for Cost of Goods Sold, the direct costs attributable to the production of the goods sold.&lt;SEP&gt;Cost of Goods Sold (COGS) is the total cost attributed to the production of goods sold by a company.&lt;SEP&gt;COGS, or Cost of Goods Sold, represents the direct costs attributable to the production of the goods sold in the report.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d5de8e1dcf9a61dbf421e8d14c5dfb81&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d7127bfda8dc54bd1f2b53807d426a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68946f49f11907e4dcbd09bd92dd464e</data>
