  <data key="d0">B2B</data>
  <data key="d1">saleschannel</data>
  <data key="d2">B2B stands for Business-to-Business, indicating transactions between businesses rather than between a business and individual consumers.&lt;SEP&gt;B2B stands for Business-to-Business, indicating sales transactions between businesses.&lt;SEP&gt;B2B is a sales channel that includes wholesale transactions with discounted pricing.</data>
