<node id="Onzenna">
  <data key="d0">Onzenna</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Onzenna is a beauty and skincare brand that operates primarily through a direct-to-consumer storefront, showcasing its products to a targeted audience. The brand has been analyzed for its sales and revenues, indicating a focus on commercial performance. In the context of marketing and social media, Onzenna is identified as a required tag for collaborations involving influencers, specifically for partnerships with the Grosmimi brand, highlighting its strategic importance in influencer marketing.

Onzenna is also recognized by its aliases, which include the Korean name 온제나, as well as the names zezebaebae and ZZBB, reflecting its diverse branding identity across different markets. It is categorized in the brands section, indicating its position within a larger portfolio.

Additionally, Onzenna operates a Gmail account for communications, facilitating email interactions, which may aid in customer service and brand outreach. As an influential entity, Onzenna supports influencer partnerships through a creator signup process and by providing sample gifting, enhancing its market presence and engagement with potential brand ambassadors. 

Furthermore, Onzenna serves as an umbrella brand that encompasses various sub-brands, representing a higher organizational structure. This strategic positioning allows Onzenna to manage, promote, and unify its brand offerings effectively within the beauty and skincare industry.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2e216433e87e27df18023b92896cdd9c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37b30a301ff091160ca40781663d92de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d7c07af37da7e5a5309a78b4b1227b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c06dd64def53a7e8da8de0bba376d516&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b748e5d4217d058fff88e8a8fca4b5e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb2d2cc010521b4bf1c2e6dc630563f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92d9eac7a8b05861fdf2bd765a1921ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7395072ce178f261136e727d265e0262</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__golmani__ref__kpi-data-taxonomy.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__golmani__ref__orbi-business-context.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__resource-finder.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__gmail_affiliate_faq_builder.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__find_resources.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__gmail_rag.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__influencer_inbound_pipeline.md&lt;SEP&gt;pipeline_dashboard_ui.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775381191</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
