<node id="Total Value">
  <data key="d0">Total Value</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Total Value is the decisive metric in an auction that determines the winner based on several weighted factors.&lt;SEP&gt;Total Value is a calculated metric used in ad auctions, composed of the advertiser bid, estimated action rate, and ad quality, which determines the winner of the auction.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47b40c2d8c8650905a9f57434cf095c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70dcbf46893fec74c116376cce3d4cf</data>
