<node id="Creative Quality">
  <data key="d0">Creative Quality</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Creative Quality refers to the effectiveness and appeal of an ad's content and presentation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47b40c2d8c8650905a9f57434cf095c4</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__ad_auctions.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314275</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cost Per Action (CPA)">
  <data key="d0">Cost Per Action (CPA)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Cost Per Action (CPA) refers to the cost incurred by advertisers for a desired user action, indicating potential inefficiencies in ad performance.&lt;SEP&gt;Cost Per Action (CPA) refers to the metric used to determine the cost-effectiveness of an ad campaign based on the desired action taken by users.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47b40c2d8c8650905a9f57434cf095c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a84cf461c30eed0176d01b34c9ddcfab</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__ad_auctions.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__performance_fluctuations.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314480</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ad Relevance Diagnostics">
  <data key="d0">Ad Relevance Diagnostics</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Ad Relevance Diagnostics refers to the process and tools used to evaluate whether advertisements are effectively reaching and engaging their target audience.&lt;SEP&gt;Ad Relevance Diagnostics are diagnostic tools used to compare ad performance against competitors, focusing on quality, engagement, and conversion metrics.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d9325aa8b09d601b506d1bfb8a0fdbf1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70dcbf46893fec74c116376cce3d4cf</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__ad_relevance_diagnostics.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__core_concepts.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314422</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quality Ranking">
  <data key="d0">Quality Ranking</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Quality Ranking is a diagnostic measure that compares the perceived quality of an ad against competitors targeting the same audience.&lt;SEP&gt;Quality Ranking measures perceived ad quality in diagnostic tools and is part of Ad Relevance Diagnostics.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d9325aa8b09d601b506d1bfb8a0fdbf1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70dcbf46893fec74c116376cce3d4cf</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__ad_relevance_diagnostics.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__core_concepts.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314422</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Engagement Rate Ranking">
  <data key="d0">Engagement Rate Ranking</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Engagement Rate Ranking is a diagnostic measure assessing expected engagement levels of an ad compared to competitors.&lt;SEP&gt;Engagement Rate Ranking assesses the expected engagement rate of an ad, serving as a diagnostic measure.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d9325aa8b09d601b506d1bfb8a0fdbf1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70dcbf46893fec74c116376cce3d4cf</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__ad_relevance_diagnostics.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__core_concepts.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314422</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Conversion Rate Ranking">
  <data key="d0">Conversion Rate Ranking</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Conversion Rate Ranking evaluates expected conversion rates relative to competitors with the same optimization goal.&lt;SEP&gt;Conversion Rate Ranking evaluates the expected conversion rate, providing insight into ad effectiveness compared to competitors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d9325aa8b09d601b506d1bfb8a0fdbf1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70dcbf46893fec74c116376cce3d4cf</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__ad_relevance_diagnostics.md&lt;SEP&gt;skill__meta-ads-agent__ref__core_concepts.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775314422</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
