<node id="Shopify Admin API">
  <data key="d0">Shopify Admin API</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The Shopify Admin API is a credential used for accessing and managing resources on Shopify platforms, specifically for gifting.&lt;SEP&gt;The Shopify Admin API allows developers to access and manage the functionality of their Shopify store programmatically.&lt;SEP&gt;Shopify Admin API is used to validate data related to customers within the Shopify system during testing.&lt;SEP&gt;The Shopify Admin API is utilized as the source for customer and order data within the Shopify platform.</data>
