  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A Workflow in n8n is a series of automated tasks defined by nodes and connections that can be updated or modified.&lt;SEP&gt;Workflow refers to a sequence of processes or steps through which a piece of work passes from initiation to completion.&lt;SEP&gt;A Workflow refers to a series of automated steps or processes within the n8n platform.</data>
