  <data key="d0">Harness Simplification 원칙</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Harness Simplification 원칙은 최대한 간단한 솔루션을 추구하는 원칙이다.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5122ca9d79dd5ae57c7c99500db14cd0</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315042</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="하위 에이전트 맵">
  <data key="d0">하위 에이전트 맵</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">하위 에이전트 맵은 특정 도메인과 기술, 역할 등을 정리하여 제시한 표이다.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5122ca9d79dd5ae57c7c99500db14cd0</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315043</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Compaction">
  <data key="d0">Compaction</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Compaction refers to the traditional method of summarizing lengthy conversations, which 제갈량 critiques for causing context anxiety.&lt;SEP&gt;Compaction refers to a method for summarizing lengthy conversations to alleviate context anxiety, but it can cause information loss.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36f10ee0781adf74fef17ac4d52aa0e0</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315043</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Context Reset">
  <data key="d0">Context Reset</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Context Reset is a method described in 제갈량's approach to manage session transitions and mitigate context anxiety in agent workflows.&lt;SEP&gt;Context Reset is a method inspired by Zhuge Liang that focuses on saving session reports to start fresh without context anxiety.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36f10ee0781adf74fef17ac4d52aa0e0</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315043</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Session Report">
  <data key="d0">Session Report</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Session Report is a structured handoff artifact that allows for a clean slate in the next session by saving previous context.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315043</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Codex">
  <data key="d0">Codex</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Codex is another editor used in conjunction with others, operating within its own context as well.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315044</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="바바">
  <data key="d0">바바</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">바바 is an editor that functions independently, similar to WJ Test1 and Codex, during multi-editor sessions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315044</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Generator">
  <data key="d0">Generator</data>
  <data key="d1">role</data>
  <data key="d2">Generator represents a sub-agent responsible for creating specifications and tasks in ORBI's system architecture.&lt;SEP&gt;Generator is a role responsible for expanding requests into full specifications and assigning tasks based on an ambitious scope.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36f10ee0781adf74fef17ac4d52aa0e0</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315044</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Orchestrator">
  <data key="d0">Orchestrator</data>
  <data key="d1">role</data>
  <data key="d2">Orchestrator is the role that breaks down the sprint, assigns agents, and distributes editors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315044</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Negotiator">
  <data key="d0">Contract Negotiator</data>
  <data key="d1">role</data>
  <data key="d2">Contract Negotiator is responsible for negotiating sprint contracts between the Generator and Evaluator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315045</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Context Manager">
  <data key="d0">Context Manager</data>
  <data key="d1">role</data>
  <data key="d2">Context Manager oversees the structured handoff and manages context resets based on session reports.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315045</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Harness Simplifier">
  <data key="d0">Harness Simplifier</data>
  <data key="d1">role</data>
  <data key="d2">Harness Simplifier removes unnecessary scaffolding during model improvements to streamline the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315045</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phase 0">
  <data key="d0">Phase 0</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Phase 0 is the scanning phase focused on assessing the current status of agents and ongoing tasks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315045</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phase 1">
  <data key="d0">Phase 1</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Phase 1 involves identifying risks and dependencies within projects through a risk matrix.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315046</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phase 2">
  <data key="d0">Phase 2</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Phase 2 is the planning stage where sprint contracts and scopes are defined.&lt;SEP&gt;Phase 2 refers to a specific step in the process where an n8n webhook receives data and interacts with the Shopify Draft Order API.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5697e39e67f1d9405f8fc22dda4faaee</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__deploy_influencer_page.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315308</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phase 3">
  <data key="d0">Phase 3</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Phase 3 is the execution phase where generators run tasks based on the defined contracts.&lt;SEP&gt;Phase 3 involves integrating Airtable with the draft order process for record updates and email notifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Phase 3 refers to the stage in the Grosmimi Gifting Application process that includes order creation, Airtable record updates, and sending email communications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5697e39e67f1d9405f8fc22dda4faaee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6e4502df455ed93d19286469452b67d</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__deploy_influencer_page.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__influencer_typeform.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315541</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phase 4">
  <data key="d0">Phase 4</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Phase 4 entails the evaluation step where outputs are verified against criteria.&lt;SEP&gt;Phase 4 involves tracking content uploads in Airtable and sending reminder emails to influencers who have not submitted content.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6e4502df455ed93d19286469452b67d</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md&lt;SEP&gt;workflow__influencer_typeform.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315541</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Phase 5">
  <data key="d0">Phase 5</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Phase 5 is the reporting phase that involves structured handoff documentation of changes and verification scores.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315046</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Anthropic Criteria">
  <data key="d0">Anthropic Criteria</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Anthropic Criteria are the standards applied to project evaluations, emphasizing function completeness.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315046</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sprint Contract">
  <data key="d0">Sprint Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Sprint Contract is an agreement between the Generator and Evaluator defining the criteria for task completion in the workflow.&lt;SEP&gt;Sprint Contract is an agreement formed before a task begins to define the scope and verification criteria for the work to be done.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5f0db10cb6ff502d03b900d2bdc7f8d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36f10ee0781adf74fef17ac4d52aa0e0</data>
  <data key="d4">skill__제갈량.md</data>
  <data key="d5">1775315047</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
