  <data key="d2">The file 'tools/data_keeper.py' is an unaffiliated tool in the tools directory.&lt;SEP&gt;tools/data_keeper.py is the name of the script being audited, which contains functionality for data management tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;tools/data_keeper.py is a Python script under evaluation for its functionality and data integrity as part of the Codex Audit process.&lt;SEP&gt;The file `tools/data_keeper.py` is the subject of the audit, which reviews its various components and logic.&lt;SEP&gt;Tools/data_keeper.py is the Python script being audited, with noted functionality and integrity issues.&lt;SEP&gt;tools/data_keeper.py is the script that underwent functionality and data integrity auditing.&lt;SEP&gt;The file tools/data_keeper.py contains the code being audited, which has encountered several issues according to the report.</data>
