<node id="Codex Audit Result">
  <data key="d0">Codex Audit Result</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Codex Audit Result is a comprehensive structured report utilized for documenting the outcomes of audits performed on various scripts, particularly within the context of financial reporting compliance. This report effectively summarizes findings even when the actual code files are not available, focusing on critical analyses of scripts such as `tools/codex_evaluator.py`, `tools/setup_n8n_delivery_email.py`, `patch_draft_gen_v2.py`, and `data_keeper.py`. It highlights issues related to financial calculations and inconsistencies identified in a company's accounting processes.

The report provides detailed evaluations of the functionality, data integrity, and quality of the analyzed code, categorizing and detailing various issues that may adversely affect operation. Specific findings include critical insights concerning COGS calculations, revenue mapping logic, and discrepancies in revenue data. These findings are essential for stakeholders to assess severity levels and gain clarity regarding the quality and functionality of the code under review.

The Codex Audit Result also encompasses documentation of pipeline audits, illustrating the status and results of these evaluations, particularly regarding the integrity and functionality of patch scripts. A notable entry relates to a pipeline audit named PIPELINER, dated 20260406_002847, further emphasizing the multifaceted nature of the report. Also, it covers audits focused on scripts responsible for advertising and sales data collection and management, hence broadening the scope of its utility. 

Ultimately, the Codex Audit Result serves as a crucial reference for stakeholders, aiding in the identification of issues and ensuring thorough oversight in financial compliance and operational auditing.&lt;SEP&gt;The Codex Audit Result provides an overview of the evaluation conducted on the script tools/data_keeper.py.&lt;SEP&gt;The Codex Audit Result summarizes the outcomes of a code evaluation for the specified script, highlighting functionality, data integrity, and code quality scores.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a8abf029ce1d1ed7ed4c55e7af10bd26&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a2e3b9dda15dc2d0f3db7938c548c4a6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-82d5e6384ec2e39cd8d8e05a2bc453df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf0e99914d3f5fa12604d552b1873776&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-205ab7c330a998ad55b9cb0fd5320d5d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2bb2184dcf276d2c10854b0f0bc061f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a05ea772fc966c7967e5b0e518ac558&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d7927dc3548bedd048eba656f5cfc08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d06f425bac82c61d59416b2891c27c80&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f0a51102d871f5d8cecb2bed696c3360&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d72451c08459b00c6cd8799579d3874d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8bad1addd0764c0c7cd3a0677bc927d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0e34eca661f2d465825cd5724fe1db9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfcd98f783316bc8eecaac4cd7288f04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4de7f333320ca174ca58ce081017887c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-219572b1eb78a67bb2e7452e32318243&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-474107f576df6a5c3d4d3875afe637ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-246e52e2d3b2a2f2c17a33d437a3b412&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d46bf96e549f6cf9637bba620110856c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb93f83f45ce2af70c37a4fa15a73f16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4beb9de386e201fd48d2d662de35eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4e4d9eae104c62cb5a0dd9ff1a2e755&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41c1e499b0a263b3c3be91169eaf658e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ab7ce837c49b802287f8f1433ef8df4</data>
